textContent:
Okay here is my character so far:

Youren
Looks roughly like me but without a beard, because I am unimaginative
Age 31 like me because I am unimaginative
Has an abundance of parents, almost too many parents, raised in a house where aunts and uncles helped out
Grew up hearing stories about Zhuren and wanted to be a hero too
Think there’s a solution for everything
Maybe Zhuren’s solution was the right one at the time, but there was a better alternative; otherwise why would the solution “run out?”
Must be a way to heal the world and balance/bring back the power, because it can’t have just gone away…
Shen was a god
You can’t just “use up” a god… gotta go somewhere
The tree Shu is probably the answer, maybe the answer is up in those branches somewhere, or at the top, or inside the trunk… it’s not the heart that I’m looking for, but a way to bring back Shen and convince him to spread the power, or maybe to decentralize the power in some other sustainable way
No idea what I’m doing, but dead end job and no girlfriend/wife or mortgage so time to head for the tree and see what I can do about this mess

Starting gear:
- 2 feet of godhair cord
- Pair of mittens
- Pair of leather gloves
- Backup pair of leather gloves
- 50 feet of rope (strong enough to rappel with)
- Poncho
- Pair of like metal climbing cleat things I can strap onto my boots, kind of like this: https://a.co/d/79ePQcq (is this okay?)
- Hammock I can wrap around a branch to sleep in
- Flint and steel/fire starter
- Small Kerosene cooking grill thing, like for camping
- Bottle of kerosene
- Wicking cotton
- Machete
- Five railroad-style iron spikes
- Mallet
- Grappling hook
- Water skein
- 3ft x 3ft waxed cloth
- Jerky and dense cakes and cheese or whatever
